DATA[Panorama]]></cmt></wpt><wpt lat="35.306899" lon="23.932947"><ele>683.0</ele><name><![CDATA[Panorama]]></name><cmt><![CDATA[Panorama]]></cmt></wpt><wpt lat="35.307069" lon="23.93347"><ele>656.0</ele><name><![CDATA[Panorama]]></name><cmt><![CDATA[Panorama]]></cmt></wpt><wpt lat="35.307246" lon="23.933836"><ele>659.0</ele><name><![CDATA[Panorama]]></name><cmt><![CDATA[Panorama]]></cmt></wpt><wpt lat="35.306991" lon="23.936375"><ele>640.0</ele><name><![CDATA[Ponto de descanso]]></name><cmt><![CDATA[Ponto de descanso]]></cmt></wpt><wpt lat="35.305382" lon="23.939518"><ele>585.0</ele><name><![CDATA[Panorama]]></name><cmt><![CDATA[Panorama]]></cmt></wpt><wpt lat="35.305253" lon="23.939697"><ele>578.0</ele><name><![CDATA[Panorama]]></name><cmt><![CDATA[Panorama]]></cmt></wpt><wpt lat="35.305205" lon="23.939662"><ele>579.0</ele><name><![CDATA[Panorama]]></name><cmt><![CDATA[Panorama]]></cmt></wpt><wpt lat="35.303886" lon="23.941673"><ele>538.0</ele><name><![CDATA[Vire a esquerda atravessando o rio]]></name><cmt><![CDATA[Vire a esquerda atravessando o rio]]></cmt></wpt><wpt lat="35.30385" lon="23.941707"><ele>551.0</ele><name><![CDATA[Interseção]]></name><cmt><![CDATA[Interseção]]></cmt></wpt><wpt lat="35.30383" lon="23.941844"><ele>546.0</ele><name><![CDATA[Panorama]]></name><cmt><![CDATA[Panorama]]></cmt></wpt><wpt lat="35.293896" lon="23.955695"><ele>365.0</ele><name><![CDATA[Panorama]]></name><cmt><![CDATA[Panorama]]></cmt></wpt><wpt lat="35.293844" lon="23.95622"><ele>365.0</ele><name><![CDATA[Panorama]]></name><cmt><![CDATA[Panorama]]></cmt></wpt><wpt lat="35.291588" lon="23.95803"><ele>339.0</ele><name><![CDATA[Panorama]]></name><cmt><![CDATA[Panorama]]></cmt></wpt><wpt lat="35.291488" lon="23.958059"><ele>341.0</ele><name><![CDATA[Panorama]]></name><cmt><![CDATA[Panorama]]></cmt></wpt><wpt lat="35.290526" lon="23.958498"><ele>326.0</ele><name><![CDATA[Panorama]]></name><cmt><![CDATA[Panorama]]></cmt></wpt><trk><name><![CDATA[Samariá Gorge]]></name><cmt><![CDATA[Um desfiladeiro lindíssimo, incrível. Uma trilha de 16km de quase totalmente de descida. Para quem tem problemas de joelho aconselho os palos, me salvaram. É incrivelmente linda. Tem várias paradas com banheiros turco e água para beber. Aconselho levar uma sandália para depois da trilha, os pés agradecem. No final do desfiladeiro, é necessário apresentar o bilhete de entrada, e mais 750m depois da saída do parque Nacional, tem um ônibus que leva até o ferry. Os tickets do ferry que leva até Sougia e do ônibus até Xyloskalo, na entrada do Gorge, podem ser comprados no café ao lado do estacionamento na entrada do Gorge. 

A beautiful, incredible gorge. A 16km trail that is almost entirely downhill. For those with knee problems, I recommend the palos, they saved me. It is incredibly beautiful. There are several stops with Turkish toilets and water to drink. I recommend taking sandals for after the trail, your feet will thank you. At the end of the gorge, you need to show your entrance ticket, and 750m after the exit of the National Park, there is a bus that takes you to the ferry. Tickets for the ferry to Sougia and the bus to Xyloskalo, at the entrance to the Gorge, can be purchased at the café next to the parking lot at the entrance to the Gorge.]]></cmt><desc><![CDATA[Um desfiladeiro lindíssimo, incrível. Uma trilha de 16km de quase totalmente de descida. Para quem tem problemas de joelho aconselho os palos, me salvaram. É incrivelmente linda. Tem várias paradas com banheiros turco e água para beber. Aconselho levar uma sandália para depois da trilha, os pés agradecem. No final do desfiladeiro, é necessário apresentar o bilhete de entrada, e mais 750m depois da saída do parque Nacional, tem um ônibus que leva até o ferry. Os tickets do ferry que leva até Sougia e do ônibus até Xyloskalo, na entrada do Gorge, podem ser comprados no café ao lado do estacionamento na entrada do Gorge. 

A beautiful, incredible gorge. A 16km trail that is almost entirely downhill. For those with knee problems, I recommend the palos, they saved me. It is incredibly beautiful. There are several stops with Turkish toilets and water to drink. I recommend taking sandals for after the trail, your feet will thank you. At the end of the gorge, you need to show your entrance ticket, and 750m after the exit of the National Park, there is a bus that takes you to the ferry. Tickets for the ferry to Sougia and the bus to Xyloskalo, at the entrance to the Gorge, can be purchased at the café next to the parking lot at the entrance to the Gorge.]]></desc><trkseg><trkpt lat="35.307812999999996" lon="23.918423999999998"><ele>1230.792</ele><time>2025-05-10T04:20:22Z</time></trkpt><trkpt lat="35.307753" lon="23.918415999999997"><ele>1230.773</ele><time>2025-05-10T04:22:20Z</time></trkpt><trkpt lat="35.307708999999996" lon="23.918403999999995"><ele>1233.520</ele><time>2025-05-10T04:23:09Z</time></trkpt><trkpt lat="35.307736999999996" lon="23.918455999999995"><ele>1232.509</ele><time>2025-05-10T04:23:39Z</time></trkpt><trkpt lat="35.307685" lon="23.918470999999997"><ele>1237.141</ele><time>2025-05-10T04:25:36Z</time></trkpt><trkpt lat="35.307628" lon="23.918479999999995"><ele>1226.360</ele><time>2025-05-10T04:26:37Z</time></trkpt><trkpt lat="35.307592" lon="23.918518999999996"><ele>1225.981</ele><time>2025-05-10T04:26:39Z</time></trkpt><trkpt lat="35.307585" lon="23.918587999999996"><ele>1223.378</ele><time>2025-05-10T04:26:43Z</time></trkpt><trkpt lat="35.307584000000006" lon="23.918652999999996"><ele>1223.521</ele><time>2025-05-10T04:26:49Z</time></trkpt><trkpt lat="35.307582000000004" lon="23.918709999999997"><ele>1226.992</ele><time>2025-05-10T04:26:58Z</time></trkpt><trkpt lat="35.307604000000005" lon="23.918764999999997"><ele>1226.984</ele><time>2025-05-10T04:27:04Z</time></trkpt><trkpt lat="35.30766200000001" lon="23.918773999999996"><ele>1222.763</ele><time>2025-05-10T04:28:27Z</